  <scopecontent id="aspace_823efa841a22bf8d9164477a89389823">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>"Cornell Class of 1944 Tales," a volume of stories and reminiscences of members of Cornell's Class of 1944. Topics include World War II, family life, careers, and memories. Also, three red Cornell blazers, six Cornell hats, three Cornell pennants, Class of 1944 t-shirt, and various pins, key chains, holiday ornament, brochures, and other memorabilia from Class Reunions over the years.</p>  </scopecontent>
